title: 1.14 Exodus II: Egypt, No!
itunes:title: Exodus II: Egypt, No!
description: After ten rounds of unpleasantness, Moses leads the Israelites out of Egypt towards Mt Sinai. They don't yet know it, but they have begun 40 years of wandering in the wilderness.
